# Panini Finance Core

## Glassbox mandate

**All problems will be solved as glassbox.**

Every problem (L1 practice explanations, L2 Glassbox Math, L2 MCQ solutions) must expose:
1. First principle / accounting or finance identity
2. Numbered derivation steps with formulas
3. Statement/market flow when relevant
4. IFRS vs US GAAP when relevant
5. Final answer + quick sanity check

## Dual level

- `l1` → `src/level1/` (93 modules, practice, formula deck) — CSS under `.level1-root`
- `l2` → deep modules in `src/data/lm##_*.js` + `MODULE_CONTENT` in `App.jsx`
- `noupload/` is local only — never commit

## When adding an L2 LM

Follow `.cursor/skills/add-cfa-module/SKILL.md` and `.cursor/skills/glassbox-problems/SKILL.md`.
